tr-param=\"volume\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\" data-addclass=\"infobox-cell-hidden\">-</span></span><span data-attr-param=\"realtime\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\" data-addclass=\"infobox-cell-hidden\">-</span></span><span data-attr-param=\"graph\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\">No data to display</span></span><span data-attr-param=\"usesinfobox\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\">Item</span></span><span data-attr-param=\"id\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Soul_fragment?action=edit\"><b>?</b> (edit)</a></span><span data-attr-index=\"1\">25196</span><span data-attr-index=\"2\">25201</span></span><span data-attr-param=\"id_smw\"><span data-attr-index=\"0\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Soul_fragment?action=edit\"><b>?</b> (edit)</a></span><span data-attr-index=\"1\">25196</span><span data-attr-index=\"2\">25201</span></span><span>Versions: 2</span><span>Default version: In-match</span></div><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"><div><span>SMW Subobject for Tutorial</span><span>Examine: Lightly pulsing with energy.</span><span>Is members only: true</span><span>Is variant of: Soul fragment</span><span>Uses infobox: Item</span><span>Image: File:Soul fragment.png</span><span>Weight: 0.000</span><span>Value: 1000</span><span>Version anchor: Tutorial</span><span>Release date: 6 January 2021</span><span>Item ID: 25196</span></div><div><span>SMW Subobject for In-match</span><span>Examine: Lightly pulsing with energy.</span><span>Is members only: true</span><span>Is variant of: Soul fragment</span><span>Uses infobox: Item</span><span>Image: File:Soul fragment.png</span><span>Weight: 0.000</span><span>Value: 1000</span><span>Version anchor: In-match</span><span>Release date: 6 January 2021</span><span>Item ID: 25201</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Soul_fragment_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Soul fragment detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Soul_fragment_detail.png/130px-Soul_fragment_detail.png?7f4ad\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"130\" height=\"149\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Soul_fragment_detail.png/195px-Soul_fragment_detail.png?7f4ad 1.5x, /images/thumb/Soul_fragment_detail.png/260px-Soul_fragment_detail.png?7f4ad 2x\" data-file-width=\"959\" data-file-height=\"1099\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Soul fragments</b> are obtained as drops from <a href=\"/w/Forgotten_Soul_(Soul_Wars)\" title=\"Forgotten Soul (Soul Wars)\">Forgotten Souls</a> during a game of <a href=\"/w/Soul_Wars\" title=\"Soul Wars\">Soul Wars</a>. They can also be obtained by killing players who possess them.\n</p><p>The fragments are used on the <a href=\"/w/Soul_Obelisk\" title=\"Soul Obelisk\">Soul Obelisk</a> to reduce the damage reduction percentage of the <a href=\"/w/Avatar_of_Creation\" title=\"Avatar of Creation\">Avatar of Creation</a> and <a href=\"/w/Avatar_of_Destruction\" title=\"Avatar of Destruction\">Destruction</a>. The team who controls the Soul Obelisk will have each soul fragment reduce the Avatar's damage reduction percentage by one, while the team that does not have control will find that sacrificing soul fragments at the Soul Obelisk will only be worth one-third of the contribution.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tutorial\">Tutorial</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Tutorial\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Tutorial\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the Soul Wars tutorial, players obtain one soul fragment as part of the demonstration. Attempting to pick up another from the ground will despawn the soul fragment from the ground, although players can cast <a href=\"/w/Telekinetic_Grab\" title=\"Telekinetic Grab\">Telekinetic Grab</a> to obtain more.\n</p><p>If the player dies during the tutorial, the soul fragment is destroyed, and they must reclaim it from <a href=\"/w/Nomad\" title=\"Nomad\">Nomad</a> to continue progressing through the tutorial.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Drop_sources\">Drop sources</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Drop sources\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Drop sources\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"seealso\">For an exhaustive list of all known sources for this item, see <span class=\"plainlinks\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Special:Ask?limit=500&amp;p%5Bformat%5D=table&amp;p%5Bmainlabel%5D=Monster&amp;po=%3FDrop+Quantity%0A%3FRarity&amp;q=%5B%5BDropped+item%3A%3ASoul+fragment%5D%5D\">here</a></span> (<span class=\"plainlinks\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Special:Ask?limit=500&amp;p%5Bformat%5D=table&amp;p%5Bmainlabel%5D=Monster&amp;po=%3FDrop+Quantity%0A%3FRarity&amp;q=%5B%5BDropped+item%3A%3ASoul+fragment%5D%5D+OR+%5B%5BDropped+item+from+RDT%3A%3ASoul+fragment%5D%5D\">include RDT</a></span>).</div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable filterable item-drops autosort=4,a\" style=\"text-align:center\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"drop-disp-btn btn-first\">Source</th><th>Level</th><th>Quantity</th><th class=\"drops-rarity-header\">Rarity</th></tr><tr style=\"text-align:center\"><td style=\"text-align:left;border-right:none\"><a href=\"/w/Forgotten_Soul_(Soul_Wars)\" title=\"Forgotten Soul (Soul Wars)\">Forgotten Soul (Soul Wars)</a></td><td class=\"\" data-sort-value=\"46\">46; 76 <span class=\"drops-combat\" style=\"margin-left:0.3em;\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\"><img alt=\"Multicombat.png\" src=\"/images/Multicombat.png?94b13\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"19\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a></span></td><td data-sort-value=\"1\">1–4</td><td data-sort-value=\"1\" class=\"table-bg-blue\"><span>Always</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Soul_fragment?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th>Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/20_January\" title=\"20 January\">20&#160;January</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Puro-Puro_Improvements_and_Barbarian_Assault_Changes\" title=\"Update:Puro-Puro Improvements and Barbarian Assault Changes\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The tutorial's soul fragment value has been changed from 1 to 1,000.\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/13_January\" title=\"13 January\">13&#160;January</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:God_Wars_Instancing_and_Soul_Wars_Improvements\" title=\"Update:God Wars Instancing and Soul Wars Improvements\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>To make the in-match item appear above others when dropped, its value has been changed from 1 to 1,000. The tutorial's soul fragment value remained unchanged.\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/6_January\" title=\"6 January\">6&#160;January</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Soul_Wars_And